data.description: Serene, peaceful, tranquil with beautiful Mountain Views is just the beginning to describe this amazing place. This lovely home is move in ready so well maintained featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, large family room, living room, kitchen and dining room open floor plan. Master bedroom with walk in closet, spacious master bath with jetted tub, walls and ceilings throughout the home are T&G. Two car attached garage including a great workshop area with lots of cabinets for storage and attic is floored for storing .The back decks are just perfect for those mountain views and watching all the wildlife in very your own mountain paradise the mountains are CALLING.
